esofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-aims-to-pierce-ukraine-defences-in-northeast-general-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F104480645.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-aims-to-pierce-ukraine-defences-in-northeast-general-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F104480645.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LinkedIn%20employees%20discovered%20a%20mysterious%20list%20of%20around%20500%20names%20over%20the%20weekend.%20On%20Monday%2C%20workers%20said%20those%20on%20the%20list%20were%20laid%20off.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22LinkedIn%20laid%20off%20over%20600%20staffers%20on%20Monday.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652da1c48bed706e837dbc2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELinkedIn%20laid%20off%20over%20600%20staffers%20on%20Monday.%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Raa%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3ESome%20workers%20at%20LinkedIn%20found%20their%20names%20on%20an%20internal%20list%20a%20day%20before%20they%20were%20laid%20off.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ETwo%20workers%20told%20Insider%20the%20list%20caused%20a%20stir%20as%20workers%20tried%20to%20figure%20out%20if%20they%20were%20on%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ELinkedIn%20announced%20it%20had%20laid%20off%20more%20than%20600%20employees%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20LinkedIn%20workers%20worried%20they%20were%20about%20to%20be%20laid%20off%20after%20a%20mysterious%20internal%20list%20of%20about%20500%20employees%20was%20discovered%20to%20be%20accessible%20by%20anyone%20at%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHours%20later%2C%20workers%20who%20had%20seen%20their%20name%20on%20the%20list%20had%20their%20worst%20fears%20confirmed%20%E2%80%94%20they%20were%20laid%20off%2C%20two%20LinkedIn%20workers%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20LinkedIn%20worker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teamblind.com%2Fpost%2FLinkedIn-Layoff-508-in-Engineering-tWCmUs8h%5C%22%3Eposted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Sunday%20night%20on%20Blind%2C%20an%20anonymous%20job-posting%20site%20that%20verifies%20workers'%20employment%20using%20their%20company%20email%2C%20about%20a%20potential%20%26quot%3Bkill%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20worker%20described%20it%2C%20of%20employees%20that%20would%20be%20impacted%20by%20an%20upcoming%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERumors%20began%20to%20swirl%20within%20the%20company%20after%20the%20worker's%20post%2C%20two%20employees%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20LinkedIn%20worker%20who%20posted%20to%20Blind%20noticed%20a%20new%20list%2C%20called%20%26quot%3BOctoberUpdate%2C%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20created%20by%20the%20company's%20human%20resources%20team%20on%20LinkedIn's%20GroupID%20tool%2C%20a%20third-party%20system%20that%20allows%20workers%20to%20add%20themselves%20and%20others%20to%20teams%20and%20can%20be%20used%20to%20create%20group%20calendar%20events%20or%20email%20chains%2C%20the%20two%20employees%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20getting%20texts%20from%20everybody%2C%20all%20my%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20LinkedIn%20workers%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BEverybody%20was%20calling%20and%20saying%20'Hey%2C%20check%20GroupID.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20LinkedIn%20worker%20said%20the%20list%20included%20hundreds%20of%20people%2C%20including%20a%20friend%20who%20later%20learned%20on%20Monday%20that%20they%20had%20been%20included%20in%20the%20layoffs%20round.%20Insider%20was%20unable%20to%20independently%20confirm%20the%20full%20list%20of%20names%20on%20the%20list%20to%20check%20if%20all%20had%20been%20impacted%20by%20the%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20LinkedIn%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20to%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20uses%20GroupID%20%26quot%3Bto%20create%20and%20manage%20distribution%20lists.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20LinkedIn%20is%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20ensuring%20all%20impacted%20employees%20are%20treated%20with%20care%20and%20respect%26quot%3B%20with%20regards%20to%20the%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20GroupID%20list%20was%20deleted%20the%20same%20day%20after%20dozens%20of%20workers%20took%20to%20the%20company's%20internal%20channel%20to%20ask%20management%20about%20the%20list%2C%20but%20management%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20list%2C%20the%20worker%20told%20Insider.%20Even%20though%20it%20had%20been%20deleted%2C%20LinkedIn%20workers%20could%20still%20see%20the%20history%20of%20the%20list%2C%20including%20the%20names%20on%20it%2C%20the%20worker%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20larger%20GroupID%20tool%20also%20became%20inaccessible%20to%20LinkedIn%20staff%20on%20Sunday%2C%20two%20workers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20heard%20that%20you%20may%20be%20experiencing%20issues%20accessing%20Go%2FGroupID%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20email%20sent%20around%204%20a.m.%20on%20Monday%20from%20the%20company's%20internal%20communications%20team%20that%20was%20viewed%20by%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20looking%20into%20it%20and%20appreciate%20your%20patience%20as%20we%20work%20through%20the%20issue.%20There%20is%20no%20ETA%20at%20the%20moment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20unclear%20why%20the%20internal%20tool%20went%20down.%20The%20two%20LinkedIn%20workers%20told%20Insider%20that%20initially%20the%20tool%20was%20slow%20to%20load%20on%20Sunday%20night%20when%20they%20checked%20it%20and%20they%20suspected%20there%20were%20too%20many%20workers%20trying%20to%20access%20the%20tool%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20took%20like%2020%20minutes%20for%20the%20tool%20to%20load%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20LinkedIn%20worker%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20tool%20is%20typically%20not%20one%20that%20a%20worker%20uses%20every%20day%2C%20but%20it%20usually%20reserved%20for%20setting%20up%20or%20joining%20different%20groups.%20%26quot%3BIt%20felt%20like%20everyone%20at%20the%20company%20was%20look