%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smoke%20rises%20after%20bombing%20of%20Israeli%20forces%20with%20warplanes%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20October%207%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6525b10d68f1d46f52adb7e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmoke%20rises%20after%20bombing%20of%20Israeli%20forces%20with%20warplanes%20in%20Gaza%20City%2C%20October%207%2C%202023.%20Another%20munition%20can%20be%20seen%20falling%20toward%20a%20target.%3Cp%3EMomen%20Faiz%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModern%20fighter%20jets%20can%20be%20quite%20accurate%20with%20unguided%20munitions%20if%20the%20conditions%20are%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Bronk%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20you're%20still%20talking%20about%20significantly%20less%20precise%20delivery%20than%20when%20using%20a%20JDAM%20or%20Paveway.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20airstrikes%20on%20an%20urban%20environment%2C%20like%20Israel's%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%2C%20precision%20is%20important%20for%20preventing%20civilian%20casualties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Blow-cost%20guidance%20kit%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20manufacturer%20Boeing%20refers%20to%20the%20JDAM%2C%20%26quot%3Bconverts%20existing%20free-fall%20bombs%20into%20accurately%20guided%20smart%20weapons%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20company%20noting%20a%20greater%20than%2095%25%20system%20reliability%20during%20testing%20and%20a%20less%20than%201.7%20meter%20Circular%20Error%20Probable%20accuracy%2C%20meaning%20a%20munition%20equipped%20with%20a%20JDAM%20is%20highly%20likely%20to%20hit%20its%20intended%20target%20rather%20than%20shift%20outside%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Israel%20did%20during%20Operation%20Guardian%20of%20the%20Walls%20in%20May%202021%2C%20its%20forces%20have%20been%20using%20JDAMs%20in%20its%20current%2C%20nonstop%20strikes%20on%20Gaza.%20Early%20last%20week%2C%20the%20country%20urgently%20requested%20more