ude%20creating%20an%20external%20advisory%20network%20for%20addressing%20opportunities%20and%20challenges%20posed%20by%20AI%2C%20educating%20city%20employees%20about%20working%20with%20AI%2C%20and%20publishing%20a%20yearly%20progress%20report.%20The%20city%20also%20intends%20on%20holding%20public%20listening%20sessions%20to%20more%20transparently%20outline%20why%20and%20how%20the%20city%20is%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20announcement%2C%20the%20city%20acknowledged%20AI%20can%20in%20some%20cases%20exhibit%20patterns%20of%20bias%20and%20discrimination.%20Many%20algorithmic%20tools%20rely%20on%20data%20that%20reflect%20biases%20in%20fields%20such%20as%20policing%20and%20housing%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Ftechnology%2F23738987%2Fracism-ai-automated-bias-discrimination-algorithm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20lead%20to%20discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20people%20of%20color%20and%20women.%20The%20plan%20introduced%20actions%20to%20help%20agencies%20evaluate%20these%20risks%20and%20ultimately%20determine%20the%20efficacy%20of%20certain%20AI%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20city%20agencies%20use%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nyc.gov%2Fassets%2Foti%2Fdownloads%2Fpdf%2Freports%2F2022-algorithmic-%2520tools-reporting.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%20algorithmic%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20around%20which%20the%20city%20said%20it%20will%20establish%20new%20policies.%20These%20tools%20are%20used%20to%20analyze%20patterns%20of%20crime%2C%20match%20applicants%20to%20schools%2C%20and%20determine%20breastfeeding%20and%20maternal%20depression%20referrals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20the%20term%20AI%20can%20cause%20anxiety%2C%20you%20hear%20it%20all%20the%20time.%20People%20think%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20Terminator-type%20figure%20come%20in%20and%20take%20over%20government%20and%20displace%20human%20beings%2C%26quot%3B%20Adams%20s