20Singh%2C%20a%20former%20FTX%20executive%20testifying%20at%20Bankman-Fried's%20criminal%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Manhattan%20federal%20court%20Monday%2C%20Singh%20testified%20about%20how%20he%20frequently%20questioned%20and%20pushed%20back%20against%20Bankman-Fried's%20spending%20sprees%20and%20investment%20decisions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20was%20almost%20always%20rebuffed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20hear%20that%20my%20opinions%20were%20already%20factored%20in%2C%20and%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20continue%20sharing%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20occasion%2C%20Singh%20said%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20told%20him%20to%20stop%20sharing%20his%20views%20in%20front%20of%20a%20group%20of%20other%20FTX%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20pretty%20humiliating%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20said%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20September%202022%2C%20though%2C%20Singh%20didn't%20know%20Bankman-Fried%20was%20making%20extravagant%20purchases%20with%20funds%20from%20FTX%20customers%20who%20remained%20unaware%20their%20money%20was%20being%20spent%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222341%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Bankman-Fried.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652cb0688bed706e837ce4f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221559%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried.%3Cp%3EAngela%20Weiss%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20Singh%20got%20here%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20faces%20a%20total%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-sbf-fraud-trial-ftx-explainer-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseven%20criminal%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20committing%20or%20conspiring%20to%20commit%20wire%20fraud%2C%20securities%20fraud%2C%20and%20money%20laundering.%20Though%20he%20has%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%2C%20several%20of%20his%20former%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%20executives%20have%20pleaded%20guilty%20and%20agreed%20to%20work%20with%20prosecutors.%20Among%20them%20are%20Singh%2C%20Caroline%20Ellison%2C%20and%20Gary%20Wang%2C%20who%20have%20each%20testified%20at%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnishad-singh-launch-ftx-sam-bankman-fried-pleads-guilty-fraud-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESingh%20pleaded%20guilty%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%20to%20six%20criminal%20charges%2C%20including%20wire%20fraud%20and%20conspiracy%20charges.%20Separately%2C%20the%20US%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20filed%20a%20civil%20complaint%20against%20Singh%20in%20February%20accusing%20him%20of%20taking%20some%20%246%20million%20from%20FTX%20for%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20use%20and%20expenditures%2C%20including%20the%20purchase%20of%20a%20multi-million%20dollar%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20for%20Singh%20told%20Insider%20at%20the%20time%20their%20defendant%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20sorry%20for%20his%20role%20in%20this%20and%20has%20accepted%20responsibility%20for%20his%20actions.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingh%20testified%20that%20he%20came%20to%20know%20Bankman-Fried%20through%20a%20friendship%20with%20the%20FTX%20founder's%20younger%20brother%2C%20Gabe%20Bankman-Fried.%20After%20graduating%20with%20electrical%20engineering%20and%20computer%20science%20degrees%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%2C%20Singh%20did%20a%20stint%20at%20Facebook%20before%20starting%20at%20Alameda%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20in%202017.%20He%20moved%20to%20FTX%20in%20mid-2019%2C%20becoming%20a%20manager%20the%20following%20year%20when%20he%20gained%20the%20title%20of%20Head%20of%20Engineering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20rose%20through%20the%20ranks%2C%20so%20did%20his%20financial%20stake.%20Singh%20testified%20that%20starting%20in%202020%2C%20he%20got%20equity%20instead%20of%20FTX%20instead%20of%20bonuses%20on%20top%20of%20his%20%24200%2C000%20annual%20salary%2C%20making%20him%20at%20one%20point%20an%20on-paper%20billionaire.%20By%202021%2C%20he%20was%20living%20with%20Bankman-Fried%20and%20other%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%20executives%20in%20a%20penthouse%20in%20the%20Bahamas%20with%20his%20girlfriend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20his%20relationship%20with%20SBF%20remained%20complex.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20always%20been%20intimidated%20by%20Sam%2C%26quot%3B%20Singh%20testified.%20%26quot%3BSam's%20a%20formidable%20character.%20Brilliant.%20And%20so%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20respect%20for%20him.%20Over%20time%2C%20that%20eroded%2C%20and%20I%20became%20distrustful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EInfighting%20over%20expenses%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20often%20disagreed%20on%20money%2C%20Singh%20testified.%20He%20said%20he%20discovered%20the%20%248%20billion%20%26quot%3Bhole%26quot%3B%20in%20FTX%20finances%20in%20September%20of%202022%20and%20found%20out%20the%20money%20had%20been%20spent%20on%20real%20estate%2C%20venture%20capital%2C%20speculative%20bets%2C%20and%20campaign%20donations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%20funds%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20directed%20spending%20of%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20on%20Genesis%2C%20a%20crypto%20mining%20company%20in%20Kazakhstan.%20He%20also%20spent%20%24200%20million%20investing%20in%20the%20venture%20capital%20firm%20Sequoia%20Capital%2C%20%24500%20million%20on%20an%20AI%20company%20called%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20%2450%20million%20on%20the%20controversial%20NFT%20company%20Yuga%20Labs%2C%20Singh%20testified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFTX%20funds%20also%20went%20toward%20%241.3%20billion%20in%20sponsorship%20deals%2C%20according%20to%20a%20spreadsheet%20introduced%20in%20trial%20evidence.%20Some%20of%20the%20biggest%20chunks%20included%20more%20than%20%24150%20million%20for%20the%20naming%20rights%20and%20other%20deals%20for%20the%20Miami%20Heat's%20arena%2C%20%24150%20million%20in%20Major%20League%20Baseball%20sponsorships%2C%20%24100%20million%20in%20promotions%20with%20League%20of%20Legends%2C%20and%20a%20%2445%20million%20sponsorship%20with%20the%20Tomorrowland%20electronic%20dance%20music%20festival.%20Bankman-Fried%20also%20spent%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20on%20endorsement%20deals%20with%20Tom%20Brady%2C%20Gisele%20B%C3%BCndchen%2C%20Steph%20Curry%2C%20Kevin%20O'Leary%2C%20and%20Larry%20David.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tom%20Brady%20(left)%20and%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20(right).%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651a465b5e3a3c00199a28e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETom%20Brady%20(left)%20and%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20(right).%20%3Cp%3EJon%20Kopaloff%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20Fatih%20Aktas%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESingh%20testified%20that%20he%20disagreed%20with%20spending%20money%20to%20partner%20with%20celebrities%2C%20only%20to%20be%20overruled%20by%20Bankman-Fried.%20Tension%20over%20the%20promotion%20strategies%20continued%20to%20boil%20when%20Bankman-Fried%20invested%20%24200%20million%20in%20K5%20Global%20after%20attending%20a%20post-Superbowl%20dinner%20hosted%20by%20the%20VC%20firm's%20founder%2C%20founder%20Michael%20Kives.%20The%20guest%20list%20at%20the%20dinner%20included%20Hillary%20Clinton%2C%20Katy%20Perry%2C%20Orlando%20Bloom%2C%20Ted%20Sarandos%2C%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20Kate%20Hudson%2C%20Leonardo%20DiCaprio%2C%20Corey%20Gamble%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Kris%20and%20Kendall%20Jenner%2C%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Bankman-Fried's%20apparent%20enthusiasm%2C%20Singh%20wasn't%20too%20impressed%20by%20the%20guest%20list.%20He%20didn't%20recognize%20the%20name%20of%20Ted%20Sarandos%2C%20Netflix's%20CEO.%20Asked%20under%20oath%20who%20Kris%20and%20Kendall%20Jenner%20are%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20honestly%20can't%20tell%20you%20what%20they%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESingh%20hated%20the%20investment%2C%20testifying%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bvalue%20extractive%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Btoxic%26quot%3B%20to%20FTX's%20culture.%20The%20former%20engineering%20chief%20said%20he%20didn't%20want%20the%20company%20to%20turn%20to%20%26quot%3Bpoliticking%20and%20social%20climbing%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20he%20thought%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20he%20raised%20his%20concerns%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20basically%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20Singh%20took%20to%20mean%20the%20deal%20could%20not%20be%20reversed%2C%20he%20testified.%20The%20Alameda%20investment%20went%20forward%20using%20FTX%20customer%20money%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20and%20Singh%20also%20quarreled%20over%20more%20administrative%20expenses.%20As%20company%20executives%20sought%20to%20move%20to%20the%20Bahamas%2C%20they%20had%20nearly%20agreed%20on%20a%20more%20affordable%20property.%20Then%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20set%20his%20sights%20on%20the%20%2435%20million%20Albany%20penthouse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSam's%20a%20fan%20of%20views%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Singh%2C%20who%20recalled%20protesting%20the%20purchase%20as%20exorbitant.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20substantial%20disagreement%20about%20whether%20we%20should%20go%20with%20it%2C%20in%20part%20because%20it's%20really%20expensive%20and%20in%20part%20because%20it's%20really%20ostentatious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20got%20his%20way%20on%20the%20penthouse%20%E2%80%94%20and%20many%20other%20things%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fftxs-nishad-singh-embarrassed-bankman-frieds-flashy-spending-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697487485000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2