Windy%20conditions%20today%20brought%20the%20mercury%20down%20to%2030.5%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20three%20notches%20below%20the%20season's%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERain%2C%20accompanied%20by%20thunder%20and%20lightning%20was%20recorded%20in%20parts%20of%20Noida%2C%20Indirapuram%2C%20south%20Delhi%20and%20east%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMahesh%20Palawat%2C%20vice%20president%20(meteorology%20and%20climate%20change)%2C%20Skymet%20Weather%2C%20in%20a%20post%20of%20X%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHeavy%20thunder%20and%20rain%20clouds%20moving%20across%20Delhi%20and%20NCR.%20From%20west%20to%20east.%20Intense%20rain%20and%20hail%20storms%20are%20possible.%20Take%20care.%26quot%3B%20In%20another%20post%2C%20he%20noted%20that%20light%20rain%20and%20cool%20winds%20have%20dropped%20the%20maximum%20temperature%20of%20Delhi%20by%205%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%2036.5%20to%2030.5%20in%20the%20last%2024%20hours.%20Minimum%20may%20also%20fall%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20slight%20nip%20in%20the%20air%20on%20Monday.%20The%20air%20quality%20index%20(AQI)%20at%209%20am%20stood%20at%20195%20but%20deteriorated%20to%20a%20poor%20category%20as%20the%2024-hour%20AQI%20at%204%20pm%20was%20recorded%20at%20207.%20However%2C%20by%207%20pm%2C%20the%20AQI%20showed%20marginal%20improvement%20to%20settle%20in%20the%20moderate%20category%20as%20the%20AQI%20read%20200.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20AQI%20between%200-50%20is%20considered%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%2C%2051-100%20%26quot%3Bsatisfactory%26quot%3B%2C%20101-200%20%26quot%3Bmoderate%26quot%3B%2C%20201-300%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%2C%20301-400%20%26quot%3Bvery%20poor%26quot%3B%20and%20401-500%20%26quot%3Bsevere%26quot%3B.%20An%20AQI%20above%20500%20falls%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20plus%26quot%3B%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20quality%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20in%20the%20moderate%20category%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20and%20poor%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20Thursday%2C%20a