declared%20nuclear%20state%2C%20Israel's%20nuclear%20weapons%20cache%20is%20an%20open%20secret%20and%20the%20Arms%20Control%20Association%20puts%20its%20number%20of%20warheads%20at%2090.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20ally%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWashington%20currently%20provides%20%243.8%20billion%20per%20year%20to%20Israel%20in%20military%20aid%20under%20a%2010-year%20agreement%20running%20until%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20delivered%20increased%20munitions%20to%20Israel%20and%20deployed%20two%20aircraft%20carriers%20to%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%20--%20the%20USS%20Gerald%20Ford%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20warship%2C%20and%20the%20USS%20Eisenhower%2C%20aimed%20at%20deterring%20not%20just%20Hamas%20but%20also%20its%20allies%20in%20Iran%20and%20Hezbollah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBritish%20defence%20analysis%20firm%20Janes%20said%20US%20aircraft%20carriers%20travel%20with%20smaller%20ships%20--%20destroyers%2C%20cruisers%2C%20submarines%20and%20support%20vessels%20--%20that%20offer%20a%20multitude%20of%20capabilities%20including%20ballistic%20missile%20protection%2C%20command-and-control%2C%20humanitarian%20assistance%2C%20evacuation%20and%20disaster%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20aircraft%20carrier%20adds%20another%2095%2C000%20tons%20of%20power%20projection%20to%20the%20point%20that%20the%20United%20States%20is%20making%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Janes%20expert%20Nick%20Brown.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHamas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20a%20diverse%20arsenal%20built%20up%20over%20many%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIts%20armed%20forces%2C%20under%20the%20name%20Al-Qassam%20Brigades%2C%20numbers%2015%2C000%20men%20according%20to%20IISS%2C%20though%20it%20notes%20Arabic%20media%20have%20put%20the%20figure%20at%2040%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20heavy%20weapons%20sourced%20from%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%20--%20particularly%20Iran%2C%20Syria%20and%20Libya%20--%20and%20has%20also%20sourced%20handguns%20and%20assault%20rifles%20from%20China%20and%20other%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20a%20variety%20of%20locally-made%2C%20improvised%20explosives%20and%20Western%20sources%20say%20enough%20drones%2C%20mines%2C%20anti-tank%20guided%20missiles%2C%20grenade%20launchers%20and%20mortar%20shells%20to%20hold%20out%20for%20a%20long%20period%2C%20though%20precise%20figures%20are%20unavailable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20its%20rockets%20are%20also%20locally%20manufactured%20and%20technologically%20rudimentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHezbollah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20already%20been%20exchanges%20across%20the%20border%20between%20Israel%20and%20Lebanon%2C%20where%20the%20Iran-backed%20militant%20group%20Hezbollah%20is%20based.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHezbollah%20can%20tie%20up%20IDF%20resources%20without%20having%20to%20fully%20commit%20to%20the%20fight%2C%20instead%20relying%20on%20occasional%20rocket%20or%20missile%20strikes%20to%20prevent%20the%20Israelis%20from%20growing%20complacent%20and%20forcing%20the%20IDF%20to%20commit%20manpower%20and%20materiel%20along%20the%20northern%20border%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Soufan%20Center%2C%20a%20US%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20group%20claimed%20to%20have%20100%2C000%20fighters.%20The%20Institute%20for%20National%20Security%20Studies%20(INSS)%2C%20an%20Israeli%20think%20tank%2C%20says%20the%20number%20is%20half%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndependent%20Middle%20East%20expert%20Eva%20Koulouriotis%20estimates%20Hezbollah%20has%2020%2C000%20highly%20trained%20fighters%20and%20a%20reserve%20of%20some%2050%2C000%20who%20have%20received%20three%20months%20of%20training%20in%20Lebanon%20and%20three%20months%20in%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EINSS%20says%20the%20group's%20arsenal%20counts%20between%20150%2C000%20and%20200%2C000%20rockets%20and%20missiles%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%26quot%3B%20of%20precision%20rockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%