e%20of%20arm-twisting%20where%20a%20wholesaler%20was%20forced%20to%20give%20up%20his%20licence%20while%20a%20firm%20was%20given%20the%20licence%20despite%20not%20qualifying%20the%20criteria%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Raju%20referred%20to%20the%20statement%20of%20Delhi%20businessman%20Dinesh%20Arora%2C%20an%20accused-turned-approver%2C%20and%20claimed%20he%20had%20told%20the%20probe%20agencies%20about%20the%20bribes%20Sisodia%20took.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Arora)%20has%20stated%20in%20his%20statement%20why%20he%20had%20not%20mentioned%20earlier%20about%20the%20role%20of%20Mr%20Sisodia%20and%20has%20said%20that%20he%20was%20afraid%20that%20he%20will%20be%20harmed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ASG%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20asked%20whether%20prior%20approval%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20prosecute%20Mr%20Sisodia%20under%20section%2017A%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%20to%20which%20Raju%20replied%20in%20the%20affirmative.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESection%2017A%20stipulates%20a%20mandatory%20requirement%20for%20a%20police%20officer%20to%20seek%20prior%20approval%20from%20the%20competent%20authority%20for%20conducting%20any%20enquiry%20or%20inquiry%20or%20investigation%20into%20any%20offence%20alleged%20to%20have%20been%20committed%20by%20a%20public%20servant%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%20(PC%20Act).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERaju%20alleged%20the%20new%20excise%20policy%20encouraged%20cartelisation%20and%20was%20designed%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20that%20consumers%20ended%20up%20paying%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20remained%20inconclusive%20and%20will%20continue%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%205%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20posed%20a%20volley%20of%20questions%20to%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20ED%20about%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy%20'scam'%20and%20asked%20the%20anti-money%20laundering%20agency%20how%20a%20case%20was%20made%20out%20against%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20had%20said%20merely%20because%20some%20lobby%20or%20pressure%20groups%20had%20sought%20a%20certain%20policy%20change%20does%20not%20imply%20there%20was%20corruption%20or%20commission%20of%20crime%20unless%20an%20element%20of%20bribery%20was%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESisodia%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20on%20February%2026%20for%20his%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20'scam'.%20He%20has%20been%20in%20custody%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20arrested%20him%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20stemming%20from%20the%20CBI%20FIR%20on%20March%209%20after%20questioning%20him%20in%20Tihar%20Jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESisodia%20resigned%20from%20the%20Delhi%20cabinet%20on%20February%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20denied%20him%20bail%20in%20the%20CBI%20case%20on%20May%2030%2C%20saying%20having%20been%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20excise%20minister%2C%20he%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh-profile%26quot%3B%20person%20who%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20influence%20the%20witnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20July%203%2C%20the%20high%20court%20had%20declined%20him%20bail%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20city%20government's%20excise%20policy%2C%20holding%20that%20the%20charges%20against%20him%20are%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%20in%20nature%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20implemented%20the%20policy%20on%20November%2017%2C%202021%20but%20scrapped%20it%20at%20the%20end%20of%20September%202022%20amid%20allegations%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697479740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fo6kuu1bg_manish-sisodia_625x300_10_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanish-sisodi