20Trump's%20vitriol%2C%20filed%20a%20motion%20arguing%20that%20the%20former%20president's%20inflammatory%20rhetoric%20threatened%20to%20undermine%20his%20trial%20for%20election%20subversion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20described%20Chutkan%20in%20public%20comments%20and%20social%20media%20posts%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfraud%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BTrump-hating%20judge%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith's%20office%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bteam%20of%20thugs%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Washington%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfilthy%20and%20crime-ridden%26quot%3B%20city%20with%20a%20population%20%26quot%3Bover%2095%25%20anti-Trump.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJohn%20Lauro%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20Trump%2C%20argued%20against%20a%20gag%20order%20during%20a%20two-hour%20hearing%20in%20federal%20court%20on%20Monday%2C%20claiming%20that%20it%20would%20infringe%20on%20Trump's%20First%20Amendment%20free%20speech%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Biden%20administration%20is%20seeking%20to%20censor%20a%20political%20candidate%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20Lauro%20said%2C%20in%20a%20reference%20to%20Trump's%20bid%20to%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%20in%20the%202024%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20trying%20to%20squelch%20political%20speech%2C%26quot%3B%20Lauro%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChutkan%20pushed%20back%2C%20saying%20Trump's%20presidential%20candidacy%20does%20not%20give%20him%20%26quot%3Bcarte%20blanche%20to%20vilify%20public%20servants%20who%20are%20simply%20doing%20their%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20what%20world%20is%20it%20permissible%20for%20a%20defendant%20to%20attack%20a%20prosecutor's%20family%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E-%20No%20trial%20delay%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShortly%20before%20the%20hearing%20began%2C%20Trump%20posted%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20platform%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BTRUMP%20GAG%20ORDER%20that%20the%20CORRUPT%20Biden%20Administration%20is%20trying%20to%2