S)%20apologised%20to%20the%20patient's%20family%20and%20said%20an%20inquiry%20had%20begun.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Hodge%2C%20Director%20of%20paramedicine%2C%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20we%20were%20made%20aware%20of%20this%20incident%2C%20we%20opened%20an%20investigation%20and%20contacted%20the%20patient's%20family.%20We%20are%20deeply%20sorry%20for%20the%20distress%20that%20this%20has%20caused%20them.%20A%20full%20review%20of%20this%20incident%20is%20being%20undertaken%2C%20and%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20comment%20any%20further%20at%20this%20stage.%20The%20colleagues%20involved%20are%20being%20supported%20appropriately%2C%20and%20we%20will%20not%20be%20commenting%20further%20about%20any%20individuals%20at%20this%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20now%20been%20reported%20that%20the%20woman%20has%20subsequently%20died.%C2%A0Durham%20Police%20told%20The%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fhome-news%2Fwoman-second-death-darlington-b2430577.html%5C%22%3E%20Independent%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20''Officers%20are%20investigating%20following%20the%20death%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20her%2050s.%20The%20death%20is%20currently%20being%20treated%20as%20unexpected%20and%20a%20postmortem%20will%20now%20be%20carried%20out.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20five%20months%20after%20a%20report%20was%20published%20alleging%20how%20North%20East%20Ambulance%20Service%20workers%20had%20concealed%20failures%20and%20withheld%20evidence%20from%20inquests.%20One%20case%20was%20highlighted%20noting%20how%20a%20paramedic%20declared%20a%20teenager%20dead%20rather%20than%20trying%20to%20perform%20CPR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%2C%20''Leadership%20dysfunction%20was%20allowed%20to%20continue%20for%20far%20too%20long%20and%20this%20had%20a%20major%20impact%20on%20how%20teams%20within%20different%20directorates%20operated.%20A%20defensiveness%20grew%20and%20affected%20team%20operations%2C%20transparency%2C%20candour%2C%20and%20judgment.%20They%20also%20clearly%20impacted%20the%20health%20and%20wellbeing%20of%20staff.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDame%20Marianne%20Griffiths%20who%20published%20the%20report%2C%20paid%20tribute%20to%20the%20families%20who%20shared%20their%20experiences%20and%20said%2C%20''It%20is%20clear%20that%20they%20are%20not%20only%20devastated%20by%20the%20loss%20of%20their%20loved%20ones%20but%20also%20by%20the%20ambulance%20service's%20response%20to%20the%20legitimate%20questions%20about%20their%20care.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697476860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-05%2Fkrki1f9g_coronavirus-hospital-generic-afp_625x300_23_May_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-wakes-up-in-hospital-after-being-declared-dead-by-ambulance-crew-4487089%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20incident%2C%20The%20North%20East%20Ambulance%20Service%20(NEAS)%20apologised%20to%20the%20patients%20family%20and%20said%20an%20inquiry%20had%20begun.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-wakes-up-in-hospital-after-being-declared-dead-by-ambulance-crew-4487089%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-wakes-up-in-hospital-after-being-declared-dead-by-ambulance-crew-4487089%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-wakes-up-in-hospital-after-being-declared-dead-by-ambulance-crew-4487089%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Calls%20mount%20to%20let%20aid%20in%20to%20besieged%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697476692000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104476566%2Cimgsize-71232.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatime