%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104476435.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20dream%20girl%20of%20Bollywood%20-%20Hema%20Malini%2C%20celebrates%20her%20birthday%20today%20and%20her%20daughters%20Esha%20and%20Ahana%20Deol%20had%20a%20big%20party%20for%20her%20which%20was%20attended%20by%20several%20B-town%20celebs%20and%20the%20actress'%20friends.%20One%20saw%20veteran%20actors%20like%20Rakesh%20Roshan%2C%20Jeetendra%2C%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20arrive%20on%20this%20special%20occasion.%20Salman%20Khan%2C%20Vidya%20Balan%2C%20Jackie%20Shroff%20were%20among%20others%20to%20who%20came%20to%20wish%20the%20actress%20on%20her%20birthday!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frekha-salman-khan-rani-mukerji-jaya-bachchan-jeetendra-and-more-celebs-attend-hema-malinis-birthday-bash-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F104476435.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AAP%20To%20Make%20Electoral%20Debut%20In%20Northeast%20By%20Contesting%20Mizoram%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20decided%20to%20make%20electoral%20debut%20in%20the%20northeast%20by%20contesting%20in%20the%20Mizoram%20assembly%20polls.%20Rajesh%20Sharma%2C%20AAP's%20northeast%20in-charge%2C%20told%20reporters%20in%20Delhi%20today%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20expand%20the%20organisation%20and%20contest%20elections%20in%20the%20northeastern%20states%20was%20made%20on%20Sunday%20at%20a%20meeting%20with%20Mr%20Kejriwal.%20A%20coordination%20committee%20and%20a%20northeast%20cell%20will%20be%20formed%20for%20organisational%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAAP%20will%20also%20participate%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Mizoram%20assembly%20elections.%20The%20details%20of%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20contested%20and%20the%20constituencies%20will%20be%20provided%20by%20the%20state%20committee%2C%20and%20an%20announcement%20regarding%20it%20will%20be%20made%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20the%20northeast%20are%20grappling%20with%20various%20issues%2C%20including%20education%2C%20healthcare%2C%20inflation%2C%20and%20unemployment%2C%20and%20they%20believe%20that%20AAP%20can%20provide%20solutions%20to%20these%20problems%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20northeast%20faces%20a%20multitude%20of%20issues%2C%20including%20rampant%20corruption%20and%20nepotism.%20The%20Chief%20Ministers%20in%20these%20states%20often%20treat%20the%20state%20as%20their%20family%20estate%2C%20and%20government%20contracts%20are%20typically%20awarded%20to%20their%20family%20members%20and%20friends%2C%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGovernment%20schools%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20roads%20are%20in%20poor%20condition%20and%20inflation%20is%20on%20the%20rise.%20Unemployment%20is%20a%20significant%20problem.%20Addressing%20these%20issues%20has%20become%20crucial%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20witnessing%20the%20party's%20track%20record%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20northeast%20believe%20that%20only%20AAP%20can%20accomplish%20these%20tasks%2C%20Mr%20Sharma%20said.%20So%20they%20want%20AAP%20to%20expand%20its%20organisation%20and%20participate%20in%20elections%20in%20all%20the%20northeastern%20states.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20states%20like%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Assam%2C%20and%20Manipur%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20power%2C%20they%20have%20initiated%20divisive%20politics%20in%20a%20forceful%20manner%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bby%20dividing%20communities%20and%20stoking%20tensions%2C%20including%20conflicts%20like%20the%20Kuki-Meitei%20dispute%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20left%20the%20people%20of%20the%20northeast%20quite%20distressed%20because%20they%20never%20support%20this%20kind%20of%20politics.%20That's%20why%20the%20AAP%20is%20determined%20to%20expand%20its%20organisation%20with%20full%20force%20in%20the%20northeastern%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697476140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fvrp0m5pk_arvind-kejriwal-1200_625x300_07_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-to-make-electoral-debut-in-northeast-by-contesting-mizoram-polls-4487097%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20decided%20to%20make%20electoral%20debut%20in%20the%20northeast%20by%20contesting%20in%20the%20Mizoram%20assembly%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-to-make-electoral-debut-in-northeast-by-contesting-mizoram-polls-4487097%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-to-make-electoral-debut-in-northeast-by-contesting-mizoram-polls-4487097%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-to-make-electoral-debut-in-northeast-by-contesting-mizoram-polls-4487097%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Daily%20Despatch%3A%20The%20Day%20War%20Almost%20Broke%20Out%20On%20Israel's%20Northern%20Border%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fcu7qmn6_daily-despatch-israelgaza-war_625x300_16_October_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFrom%20the%20frontlines%20of%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20war%2C%20NDTV%20brings%20you%20daily%20despatches%20by%20journalist%20Allan%20Sorensen%2C%20Middle%20East%20Correspondent%20for%20Danish%20newspaper%20Kristeligt%20Dagblad%2C%20giving%20insights%20and%20gripping%20first-hand%20accounts%20from%20the%20war-torn%20region.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20anti-tank%20missile%20after%20the%20other%20was%20fired%20from%20Lebanon%20into%20Israel%20on%20Sunday.%20In%20at%20least%20six%20such%20attacks%20two%20Israeli%20soldiers%20were%20killed%2C%20and%20several%20others%20wounded.%20On%20Sunday%20afternoon%20it%20seemed%20as%20if%20an%20all-out%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20Lebanese%20Hezbollah%20was%20more%20likely%20than%20an%20Israeli%20land%20invasion%20of%20Gaza.%20Helicopters%2C%20drones%2C%20and%20fighter%20jets%20patrolled%20the%20clouded%20skies%20above%20the%20northern%20border%20of%20Israel%2C%20while%20the%20Israeli%20army%20ordered%20the%20evacuation%20of%20all%20villages%20within%20two%20kilometers%20of%20the%20Lebanese%20border.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20headquarters%20of%20the%20UN%20peacekeeping%20mission%20in%20southern%20Lebanon%20in%20the%20coastal%20town%20of%20Naqoura%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20rocket%20during%20the%20exchange%20of%20fire%20and%20escalation%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah.%20None%20were%20hurt%20in%20the%20attack%20and%20till%20now%20it%20has%20not%20been%20established%20where%20the%20rocket%20was%20fired%20from.%20The%20UN%20mission%2C%20known%20as%20UNIFIL%2C%20was%20created%20in%202006%20after%20a%20long%20summer%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20de-escalate%20the%20tension%20on%20the%20border%2C%20Israeli%20Defense%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20sent%20a%20clear%20message%20to%20Hezbollah.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20no%20interest%20in%20a%20war%20in%20the%20north%2C%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20escalate%20the%20situation.%20If%20Hezbollah%20chooses%20the%20path%20of%20war%2C%20it%20will%20pay%20a%20very%20heavy%20price.%20But%20if%20it%20restrains%20itself%2C%20we'll%20respect%20the%20situation%20and%20keep%20things%20the%20way%20they%20are%2C%20despite%20shooting%20from%20both%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20video%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20while%20Israel%20was%20still%20preparing%20for%20a%20land%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%2C%20the%20local%20Palestinian%20population%20was%20still%20struggling%20to%20flee%20from%20northern%20Gaza.%20It%20is%20estimated%20that%20at%20least%20one%20million%20Palestinians%20inside%20Gaza%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced.%20Some%206%2C00%2C000%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20left%20the%20northern%20areas%20following%20an%20Israeli%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUNRWA%2C%20the%20UN's%20Palestinian%20refugee%20agency%2C%20stated%20Sunday%20that%20Gaza%20%26quot%3Bis%20being%20strangled%26quot%3B%20while%20the%20number%20of%20people%20seeking%20shelter%20at%20their%20schools%20and%20facilities%20in%20the%20south%20of%20Gaza%20is%20steadily%20growing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20army%20stated%20that%20it%20would%20not%20target%20a%20specific%20route%20south%20for%20several%20hours%2C%20again%20urging%20Palestinians%20to%20leave%20the%20north.%20According%20to%20Israeli%20media%2C%20the%20request%20to%20the%20population%20in%20Gaza%20has%20two%20different%20aims.%20One%20is%20to%20clear%20the%20northern%20areas%20ahead%20of%20an%20expected%20ground%20invasion.%20The%20second%20is%20to%20maximize%20the%20pressure%20on%20Hamas%20by%20creating%20a%20situation%20that%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20a%20humanitarian%20catastrophe.%20Israel%20hopes%20that%20Hamas%20will%20release%20some%20of%20the%20199%20kidnapped%20Israelis%20inside%20Gaza%20in%20exchange%20for%20immediate%20humanitarian%20assistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHospitals%20in%20Gaza%20are%20expected%20to%20run%20out%20of%20fuel%20for%20emergency%20generations%20within%20a%20few%20days%2C%20according%20to%20the%20UN%2C%20putting%20at%20immediate%20risk%20the%20lives%20of%20a%20large%20number%20of%20patients.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20the%20Biden%20administration%20does%20not%20support%20the%20mass%20relocation%20of%20Palestinians%20outside%20of%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20heard%20directly%20from%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20President%20%5BMahmoud%5D%20Abbas%20and%20from%20virtually%20every%20other%20leader%20that%20I've%20talked%20to%20in%20the%20region%2C%20that%20that%20idea%20is%20a%20non-starter%2C%20and%20so%20we%20do%20not%20support%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Al%20Arabiya%20from%20Cairo.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20people%20should%20be%20able%20to%20stay%20in%20Gaza%2C%20their%20home.%20But%20we%20also%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20they're%20out%20of%20harm's%20way%20and%20that%20they're%20getting%20the%20assistance%20they%20need.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20on%20Sunday%20met%20with%20the%20relatives%20of%20hostages%20held%20in%20Gaza.%20Netanyahu%20made%20a%20promise%20to%20declare%20the%20release%20of%20the%20hostages%20a%20clear%20aim%20of%20the%20current%20war%20against%20Hamas.%20The%20decision%20was%20received%20with%20relief%20by%20the%20relatives%20of%20the%20hostages.%20According%20to%20Israeli%20media%20reports%2C%20negotiations%20for%20the%20release%20of%20children%2C%20women%2C%20and%20elderly%20from%20Gaza%20is%20ongoing%20with%20Qatar%20as%20a%20mediator.%20No%20details%20have%20been%20published%20about%20the%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20death%20count%20on%20the%20Israeli%20side%20stands%20at%20more%20than%201%2C300%2C%20while%20the%20number%20of%20dead%20in%20Gaza%20climbed%20to%20at%20least%202%2C670%20on%20Sunday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20US%20State%20Department%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Americans%20killed%20since%20the%20outbreak%20of%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20rose%20to%2030%20on%20Sunday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20time%2C%20we%20can%20confirm%20the%20deaths%20of%2030%20US%20citizens.%20We%20extend%20our%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20the%20victims%20and%20to%20the%20families%20of%20all%20those%20affected%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20State%20Department%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAntonio%20Guterres%2C%20UN%20Secretary-General%2C%20warned%20that%20the%20Middle%20East%20is%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20verge%20of%20the%20abyss%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHet%20urged%20Hamas%20to%20release%20hostages%20and%20pledged%20that%20Israel%20would%20allow%20humanitarian%20aid%20into%20besieged%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20one%20of%20these%20two%20objectives%20is%20valid%20in%20themselves.%20They%20should%20not%20become%20bargaining%20chips%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UN%20chief%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20said%20Sunday%20that%20he%20would%20seek%20to%20assemble%20a%20%26quot%3Bgenerous%26quot%3B%20package%20of%20wartime%20aid%20for%20Israel%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20Senate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmerica%20will%20stand%20with%20its%20ally%20Israel.%20I%2C%20along%20with%20my%20colleagues%20here%2C%20will%20lead%20the%20effort%20in%20the%20United%20States%20Senate%20to%20provide%20Israel%20with%20the%20support%20required%20to%20fully%20defend%20itself%20from%20this%20monstrous%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20news%20conference%20in%20Israel.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%2060%20Minutes%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20stated%20that%20he%20believes%20Hamas%20must%20be%20eliminated.%20He%20also%20said%20it%20would%20be%20a%20mistake%20for%20Israel%20to%20reoccupy%20parts%20of%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUp%20until%202005%2C%20some%208%2C000%20Israeli%20Jews%20lived%20in%20settlements%20inside%20Gaza.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunday%20also%20marked%20the%20day%20when%20several%20incidents%20against%20Jews%20were%20reported%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFBI%20officials%20said%20they%20had%20noticed%20an%20increase%20in%20threatening%20rhetoric%20against%20Jewish%20and%20Muslim%20communities%20in%20the%20week%20since%20the%20brutal%20Hamas%20attacks%20in%20Israel.%20In%20Germany%2C%20the%20Jewish%20symbol%2C%20the%20Star%20of%20David%2C%20was%20painted%20on%20the%20doors%20of%20several%20Jewish%20families%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Berlin.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Allan%20Sorensen%20is%20the%20Middle%20East%20correspondent%20for%20the%20Danish%20daily%20newspaper%20Kristeligt%20Dagblad.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697475720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Ft2vm2f68_daily-despatch-israelgaza-war_625x300_16_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdaily-despatch-the-day-war-almost-broke-out-on-israels-northern-border-4487066%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20anti-tank%20missile%20after%20the%20other%20was%20fired%20from%20Lebanon%20into%20Israel%20on%20Sunday.%20In%20at%20least%20six%20such%20attacks%20two%20Israeli%20soldiers%20were%20killed%2C%20and%20several%20others%20wounded.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdaily-despatch-the-day-war-almost-broke-out-on-israels-northern-border-4487066%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rachel%20Riley%20condemns%20'hideous'%20and%20'unthinkable'%20Israel-Hamas%20war%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697475360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-rachel-riley-women-of-the-year_6323570.jpg%3F20231016175630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frachel-riley-condemns-hideous-and-unthinkable-israel-hamas-war-12985744%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rachel%20Riley%20says%20it's%20difficult%20to%20witness%20the%20%26quot