isible''%20Scratch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20inevitable%20part%20of%20renting%20a%20property%20is%20dealing%20with%20the%20landlords.%20However%2C%20many%20times%2C%20landlords%20put%20up%20weird%20conditions%2C%20demands%2C%20and%20requests%2C%20that%20leave%20renters%20scratching%20their%20heads.%20One%20such%20tenant%20in%20Sydney%20was%20left%20stunned%20after%20their%20landlord%20demanded%20them%20to%C2%A0pay%20%241000%20(Rs%2052%2C743)%20for%20a%20small%20scratch%20on%20a%20wooden%20floor%20panel.%20The%20landlord%20claimed%20that%20she%20would%20need%20to%20replace%20all%20the%20floorboards%20because%20of%20the%20damage%20incurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tenant%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20username%20'BabyButtercup'%20wrote%20on%20Reddit%2C%20''Just%20want%20to%20ask%20if%20it%20sounds%20ridiculous%20to%20you%20that%20my%20landlord%20wants%20to%20charge%20%241000%20for%20a%20minimal%20scratch%20on%20a%20panel%20of%20a%20timber%20floor%3F%20Her%20plan%20is%20to%20remove%20and%20redo%20the%20whole%20flooring%20because%20I've%20unintentionally%20made%20a%20scratch%20on%20a%20panel%2C%20I%20repeat%2C%20a%20minimal%20almost%20invisible%20scratch%20on%20one%20of%20the%20panels.%20Does%20that%20make%20sense%20to%20you%3F''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22316%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Faustralia%2Fcomments%2F16zebsa%2Flandlord_wants_to_charge_1000_for_a_scratch_mark%2F%5C%22%3ELandlord%20wants%20to%20charge%20%241000%20for%20a%20scratch%20mark%20on%20a%20panel%20of%20timber%20wood%20floor%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2FBabyButt3rcup%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2FBabyButt3rcup%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Faustralia%2F%5C%22%3Eaustralia%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EMany%20on%20Reddit%20called%20the%20landlord's%20demand%20''ridiculous''.%20One%20user%20wrote%2C%20''If%20it's%20careless%20damage%20the%20tenant%20could%20be%20up%20for%20paying%20%E2%80%A6%20but%20%241k%20seems%20excessive%20if%20it's%20not%20a%20large%20scratch.''%20Another%20commented%2C%20''Sounds%20like%20she's%20trying%20to%20use%20your%20cash%20to%20fund%20a%20new%20floor.''%20A%20third%20added%2C%20''She%20wants%20new%20timber%20flooring%20and%20is%20using%20you%20to%20subsidise%20it.%20Tell%20her%20no%20and%20if%20she%20threatens%20to%20take%20it%20out%20of%20your%20bond%20challenge%20her%20at%20your%20state's%20rental%20tribunal%20as%20it%20would%20probably%20come%20under%20under%20reasonable%20wear%20and%20tear.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20renter%20and%20their%20partner%2C%20in%20a%20separate%20post%2C%20said%20that%20they%20would%20be%20going%20to%20the%20NSW%20Civil%20and%20Administrative%20Tribunal%20(NCAT)%20as%20they%20''didn't%20agree''%20with%20paying%20%241000.%C2%A0However%2C%20they%C2%A0eventually%20reached%20an%20agreement%20to%20pay%20%24500%20to%20the%20landlord%20and%20to%20drop%20their%20NCAT%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20shared%20pictures%20of%20the%20floor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Faustralia%2Fcomments%2F17538ao%2Fupdate_landlord_wants_to_charge_1000_for_a%2F%5C%22%3EUpdate%3A%20Landlord%20wants%20to%20charge%20%241000%20for%20a%20scratch%20mark%20on%20a%20panel%20of%20timber%20wood%20floor%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%20by%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2FBabyButt3rcup%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2FBabyButt3rcup%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2Faustralia%2F%5C%22%3Eaustralia%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''Initially%2C%20I%20didn't%20wanna%20pay%20%24500%20and%20insisted%20on%20going%20for%20NCAT%20and%20my%20partner%20agreed%20but%20after%20two%20days%20he%20asked%20me%20if%20we%20could%20close%20the%20case%20and%20just%20pay%20them%20%24500%20because%20he%20doesn't%20wanna%20waste%20his%20time%20going%20for%20the%20NCAT.%20I%20was%20upset%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20fight%20but%20he%20didn't%20and%20it%20makes%20sense%20that%20it%20wasn't%20worth%20anyone's%20time.%20We%20decided%20to%20close%20the%20case%20with%20the%20agents%20and%20paid%20%24500.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20have%20a%20look%20at%20the%20photos%20and%20let%20me%20know%20if%20the%20scratch%20worth%20%24500%20because%20for%20me%20it's%20not.%20Also%2C%20I%20found%20out%20that%20the%20premises%20have%20already%20been%20rented%20out%20again%20so%20does%20the%20owner%20wanna%20do%20the%20flooring%20while%20there%20are%20new%20tenants%20staying%3F%20Any%20of%20these%20doesn't%20make%20any%20sense.%20They%20even%20had%20the%20audacity%20to%20complain%20about%20the%20blind%20saying%20it%20wasn't%20tracking%20properly%20which%20wasn't%20even%20true.%20I%20hope%20she%20spends%20that%20%24500%20well%20bec%20if%20I%20wasn't%20with%20my%20partner%2C%20I%20would've%20gone%20to%20court%2C''%20the%20tenant%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697473800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fq49kb8po_floor-scratch-_625x300_16_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fsydney-landlord-asks-tenant-to-pay-rs-52-000-for-almost-invisible-floor-scratch-4486940%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20landlord%20claimed%20she%20would%20need%20to%20replace%20all%20the%20floorboards%20because%20of%20the%20damage%20incurred.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fsydney-landlord-asks-tenant-to-pay-rs-52-000-for-almost-invisible-floor-scratch-4486940%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fsydney-landlord-asks-tenant-to-pay-rs-52-000-for-almost-invisible-floor-scratch-4486940%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22