d.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''I%20didn't%20even%20ask%20the%20price%20of%20the%20tables%20%E2%80%93%20but%20this%20was%20turned%20down.%20What%20reason%20would%20they%20really%20have%20to%20say%20no%3F%20I%20wasn't%20causing%20trouble%20or%20shouting%3B%20I%20didn't%20flare%20up%20or%20swear%2C''%20Mr%20Berko%20explained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20his%20brush%20with%20racism%2C%20he%20said%2C%20''In%20my%20field%2C%20I'm%20used%20to%20dealing%20with%20racism.%20In%20this%20country%2C%20it's%20always%20indirect%20and%20never%20direct.%20For%20example%2C%20I've%20been%20stopped%20by%20the%20police%20so%20many%20times%20for%20no%20reason%20other%20than%20the%20car%20I%20drive.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E''But%20I%20could%20not%20believe%20my%20eyes%20when%20the%20staff%20member%20took%20my%20friends%20and%20out%20of%20the%20queue%20-%20making%20everyone%20look%20at%20us%20as%20if%20we%20were%20troublemakers%20%E2%80%93%20then%20let%20in%20all%20white%20people%20and%20not%20us.%20I%20haven't%20slept%3B%20I%20felt%20so%20violated%2C''%20Mr%20Berko%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr.%20Berko's%20allegations%20went%20viral%2C%20several%20people%20thronged%20100%20Wardour%20Street's%20Instagram%20page%20and%20criticised%20them.%20The%20restaurant%20later%20posted%20photographs%20of%20Black%20women%20in%20their%20stories%2C%20which%20many%20including%C2%A0Lamar%20Berko%20felt%20was%20making%20a%20''mockery''%20of%20the%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20user%20on%20one%20of%20their%20posts%20wrote%2C%20''Racism%20in%202023!%20This%20is%20extremely%20disappointing!!!%20And%20it%20seems%20whoever%20is%20running%20this%20account%20fails%20to%20see%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20issue.%20Posting%20black%20people%20on%20your%20story%20is%20a%20complete%20mockery.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697470680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Foed4d42o_lamar-berko-_625x300_16_October_23.jpg%22