he-199-hostages-12985556%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Issues%20Notice%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Secretariat%20Over%20Raghav%20Chadha's%20Indefinite%20Suspension%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08091452%2FUntitled-design.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2016%2C%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20secretariat%20in%20connection%20with%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%E2%80%99s%20plea%20questioning%20his%20indefinite%20suspension%20from%20the%20House%20pending%20an%20inquiry%20by%20the%20Privileges%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20will%20be%20next%20heard%20on%20October%2030.%20Both%20Rajya%20Sabha%20secretariat%20and%20its%20chairperson%2C%20Jagdeep%20Dhankar%2C%20are%20respondents%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChadha%20was%20suspended%20from%20the%20House%20starting%20August%2011%20for%20an%20indefinite%20period%20until%20the%20Privileges%20Committee%2C%20which%20is%20probing%20the%20matter%2C%20submits%20its%20report.%20His%20suspension%20came%20after%20five%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20accused%20Chadha%20of%20mentioning%20their%20names%20without%20their%20consent%20in%20the%20motion%20that%20sought%20a%20select%20committee%20to%20examine%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-services-bill-rajya-sabha-arvind-kejriwal-centre-ias-officer-amit-shah%5C%22%3EGovernment%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%202023.%20S.%20Phangnon%20Konyak%2C%20Narhari%20Amin%2C%20and%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%3B%20M.%20Thambidurai%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Anna%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(AIADMK)%3B%20and%20Sasmit%20Patra%20of%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20levelled%20the%20allegation%20against%20the%20AAP%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20contentious%20Bill%20(now%20law)%20was%20passed%20by%20both%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20replacing%20the%20Ordinance%20pertaining%20to%20the%20transfer%20and%20posting%20of%20senior%20officials%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government.%20The%20legislation%20received%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20assent%20on%20August%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Rakesh%20Dwivedi%2C%20appearing%20for%20Chadha%2C%20told%20the%20court%20that%20there%20have%20been%2011%20instances%20in%20the%20last%2075%20years%20where%20MPs%20included%20the%20names%20of%20their%20fellow%20MPs%20who%20were%20unwilling%20to%20be%20part%20of%20motions.%20And%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20those%20names%20were%20merely%20dropped%20without%20slapping%20a%20suspension%20order%20against%20the%20MPs%20in%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20argued%20that%20according%20to%20the%20Rules%20of%20Conduct%20of%20Business%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20the%20MP%20can%20be%20suspended%20only%20for%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20particular%20session%20%E2%80%93%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20Monsoon%20Session.%20Suspension%20of%20an%20MP%20beyond%20a%20session%20is%20not%20only%20against%20the%20rules%20but%20also%20amounts%20to%20expulsion%20of%20the%20MP%20from%20the%20House%2C%20and%20in%20effect%2C%20creates%20a%20vacancy%20in%20the%20House%2C%20Dwivedi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20underscoring%20his%20point%2C%20Dwivedi%20pointed%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20in%20the%202022%20case%20of%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F194799097%2F%5C%22%3EAshish%20Shelar%20vs%20State%20of%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20held%20that%20a%20member%20of%20the%20House%20cannot%20be%20suspended%20beyond%20a%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fsc-seeks-rajya-sabha-secretariats-reply-on-aap-mp-raghav-chadhas-plea-against-indefinite-suspension-2728503%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dwivedi%20said%20Chadha%E2%80%99s%20indefinite%20suspension%2C%20beyond%20the%20Monsoon%20session%2C%20is%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%2C%20manifestly%20arbitrary%2C%20unconstitutional%2C%20and%20erosive%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20effective%20representation%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Punjab%E2%80%9D.%20Chadha%20is%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Punjab%2C%20where%20AAP%20is%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20suspension%2C%20Chadha%20said%20in%20his%20petition%20that%20he%20is%20not%20able%20to%20attend%20the%20meetings%20of%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Finance%20and%20the%20Committee%20on%20Subordinate%20Legislation%2C%20of%20which%20he%20is%20a%20member.%20The%20work%20of%20parliament%20committees%20continues%20even%20when%20the%20House%20is%20not%20in%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20suspension%20serves%20as%20a%20stark%20message%20from%20the%20BJP%20to%20today%E2%80%99s%20youth%3A%20If%20you%20dare%20to%20ask%20questions%2C%20we%20will%20crush%20your%20voice.%20I%20was%20suspended%20for%20asking%20tough%20questions%20that%20left%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20party%2C%20without%20answers%20through%20my%20speech%20in%20Parliament%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20Bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chadha%20had%20said%20after%20his%20suspension%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-issues-notice-to-rajya-sabha-secretariat-over-aap-mp-raghav-chadhas-suspension-101697447417579.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697458370000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F08091452%2FUntitled-design.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-issues-notice-to-rajya-sabha-secretariat-over-raghav-chadhas-indefinite-suspension%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20AAP%20MP%20has%20