400%20stations%2C%20privatise%20of%2090%20trains%20and%2015%20railway%20stadiums.%20In%20fact%2C%20development%20of%20stations%20is%20a%20significant%20part%20of%20monetisation%20plans%2C%20over%2050%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20has%20it%20that%20according%20to%20the%20NITI%20Aayog%2C%20the%20government%20has%20monetised%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2026%2C000%20crore%20during%20FY24%20against%20the%20target%20of%20Rs%201.6%20lakh%20crore%20for%20the%20current%20fiscal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20senior%20officials%20at%20the%20Railways%20told%20%3Cem%3EDH%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20sector%20has%20got%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20leeway%20from%20the%20government%20and%20that%20other%20sectors%20have%20done%20better.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frailways-telecom-petrol-asset-monetisation-targets-miss%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20the%20mining%20industry%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20core%20industries%20of%20the%20economy%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20making%20up%20for%20the%20poor%20show%20of%20the%20Railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frailways-telecom-petrol-asset-monetisation-targets-miss%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehad%20reported%20that%20the%20Railways%2C%20telecom%20and%20petroleum%20sectors%20are%20unlikely%20to%20meet%20their%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20in%20an%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Finterview-p-chidambaram-national-monetisation-pipeline%5C%22%3E%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20former%20finance%20minister%20P.%20Chidambaram%20had%20noted%20that%20the%20NMP%20brought%20with%20itself%20concerns%20on%20corporate%20favouritism%2C%20rising%20costs%20for%20users%20and