can%20ignore%20the%20tremendous%20suffering%20of%20their%20fellow%20humans%20in%20crisis%20and%20carry%20on%20enjoying%20themselves.%20A%20recent%20case%20in%20point%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20the%20Indo-Pak%20World%20Cup%20match%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20October%2014%20that%20millions%20in%20India%20watched%20and%20celebrated%20even%20as%20two%20million%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20suffer%20what%20might%20well%20be%20called%20a%20second%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Funispal%2Fabout-the-nakba%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enakba%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20wonder%20if%20the%20noise%20of%20the%20celebratory%20firecrackers%20right%20after%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%E2%80%99s%20win%20reminded%20anyone%20in%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%20or%20those%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20their%20TV%20screens%20%E2%80%93%20even%20faintly%20%E2%80%93%20of%20the%20Israeli%20bombs%20that%20have%20been%20exploding%20in%20Gaza%20for%20the%20last%20several%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20the%20much-awaited%20Indo-Pak%20match%2C%20however%2C%20about%20150%20citizens%20gathered%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%20to%20protest%20Israeli%20atrocities%20in%20Palestine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20empathy%20for%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20countrymen%20and%20countrywomen%20seems%20to%20have%20dipped%20to%20an%20all-time%20low%2C%20it%20was%20heartening%20to%20see%20a%20group%20of%20people%2C%20however%20small%2C%20express%20solidarity%20for%20the%20suffering%20millions%20in%20another%20country.%20A%20genuine%20example%20of%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVasudeva%20Kutumbakam%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(The%20World%20Is%20One%20Family)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20words%20that%20our%20prime%20minister%20loves%20to%20bandy%20about%20on%20almost%20every%20international%20platform.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHolding%20up%20a%20poster%20showing%20the%20progression%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20occupation%20of%20Palestine%20from%201946%20to%202010%2C%20Maimoona%20Mollah%20from%20the%20All%20India%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Development%20Association%20(AIDWA)%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRight%20now%2C%20the%20Palestinians%20are%20being%20criticised%20as%20terrorists.%20If%20you%20take%20away%20people%E2%80%99s%20rights%2C%20even%20their%20right%20to%20live%20in%20their%20own%20homes%2C%20then%20they%20will%20retaliate.%20Israel%20did%20not%20take%20away%20the%20Palestinians%E2%80%99%20land%20by%20touching%20their%20feet%20and%20with%20love%2C%20did%20they%3F%20They%20have%20done%20it%20with%20brutal%20force%20all%20these%2075%20years.%20Yes%2C%20we%20condemn%20the%20retaliation%20and%20the%20killing%20of%20innocents%20in%20Israel%2C%20but%20innocents%20are%20being%20killed%20in%20Gaza%20too!%20And%20so%2C%20the%20killing%20has%20to%20be%20condemned%20on%20both%20sides!%20Having%20said%20that%2C%20the%20Palestinian%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20for%20self-determination%20and%20their%20homeland%20is%20very%20valid%20and%20just.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16125127%2F20231014_131959.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16125127%2F20231014_131959.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16125127%2F20231014_131959-300x169.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680302%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20woman%20holds%20up%20a%20poster%20showing%20the%20progression%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20occupation%20of%20Palestine%20from%201946%20to%202010.%20Photo%3A%20Rohit%20Kumar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMollah%20reminded%20the%20gathering%3A%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20was%20once%20a%20very%20important%20member%20of%20the%20Non-Aligned%20Movement.%20We%20have%20always%20supported%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20so%20it%20is%20very%20worrying%20that%20in%20recent%20years%20we%20are%20no%20longer%20standing%20with%20the%20oppressed%20and%20the%20persecuted%20like%20we%20used%20to.%20Just%20as%20we%20stood%20with%20the%20oppressed%20in%20South%20Africa%20and%20spoke%20out%20against%20apartheid%2C%20we%20have%20also%20stood%20up%20against%20Zionist%20apartheid!%20But%20today%20it%20is%20very%20sad%20that%20we%20are%20kowtowing%20to%20American%20and%20Israeli%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edadagiri%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(bullying).%20Even%20if%20our%20political%20class%20is%20leaning%20away%20from%20the%20principles%20that%20have%20defined%20us%2C%20at%20least%20we%20the%20people%20of%20India%20should%20stand%20for%20Palestine%2C%20and%20for%20all%20people%20on%20this%20earth%20who%20are%20oppressed.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENaveen%20Srivastava%2C%20an%20engineer%2C%20and%20political%20commentator%2C%20practically%20gave%20a%20small%20history%20class%20about%20the%20Palestine%20crisis%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CLet%20us%20not%20forget%20that%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20situation%20is%20primarily%20a%20battle%20between%20capitalism%20and%20socialism.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20religious%20war%20as%20the%20BJP%20government%20is%20trying%20to%20portray%20it!%20The%20Palestinians%E2%80%99%20land%20has%20been%20stolen%20from%20them%20over%20the%20decades%2C%20and%20today%20they%20are%20living%20in%2C%20as%20the%20international%20media%20calls%20it%2C%20an%20%E2%80%98open-air%20prison%E2%80%99.%20India%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20Palestine%20began%20in%201931%20when%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20first%20espoused%20the%20Palestine%20cause%20in%20a%20newspaper%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Jewish%20Chronicle%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20He%20reiterated%20this%20again%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHarijan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20magazine%20in%201938%20when%20he%20said%20that%20Palestine%20belongs%20to%20the%20Palestinians%20just%20as%20much%20as%20England%20belongs%20to%20the%20English.%20In%20fact%2C%20India%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20recognise%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20when%20it%20was%20first%20established%20in%201948!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20prime%20minister%20lauds%20the%20%E2%80%98nationalism%E2%80%99%20of%20Israel%2C%20but%20what%20about%20the%20nationalism%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20who%20have%20endured%20tremendous%20suffering%20for%20the%20last%20seven%20decades%3F%20The%20Palestinian%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20is%20our%20struggle%20too%20because%20the%20same%20types%20of%20fundamentalist%20forces%20are%20trying%20to%20divide%20our%20country%20on%20religious%20lines%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16125117%2F20231014_131946.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16125117%2F20231014_131946.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16125117%2F20231014_131946-300x169.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680301%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22563%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Rohit%20Kumar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubash%20Chandran%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20advocate%2C%20also%20pointed%20out%20how%20%E2%80%9Cthe%2