.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fgovernment-intervention-sought-as-oil-stock-nears-zero-at-retail-outlets%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EImphal%20Free%20Press%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cninety%20percent%20of%20the%20retail%20outlets%20and%20underground%20tanks%20are%20drying%20out%20(except%20for%20dead%20stock)%20and%20only%20a%20few%20retail%20outlets%20are%20having%20maximum%20stock%20which%20will%20run%20out%20in%20three%20or%20four%20days%20maximum%2C%20especially%20the%20petrol%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20report%20said%20the%20meeting%20was%20jointly%20called%20by%20Drivers%E2%80%99%20Association%20of%20POL%2C%20POL%20Transport%20bulk%20LPG%20and%20petroleum%20dealers%20of%20Manipur%20where%20%E2%80%9Caggrieved%20dealers%E2%80%9D%20spoke%20of%20facing%20issues%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Csevere%20nature%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20arterial%20highway%20that%20connects%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Jiribam%20to%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%20through%20the%20tribal-dominated%20districts%20of%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Tamenglong.%20The%20report%20said%20those%20issues%20%E2%80%9Cinvolve%20firing%20gun%20bullets%20at%20the%20vehicles%2C%20several%20physical%20assault%20or%20harassment%20and%20rampant%20exorbitant%20extortion%20at%20multiple%20areas%20which%20is%20increasing%20day%20by%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20continuing%20strife%20between%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20communities%20dominant%20in%20the%20hill%20and%20valley%20areas%20respectively%2C%20some%20powerful%20Kuki%20civil%20society%20organisations%20like%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Unity%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmanipur-blockade-of-vital-national-highway-continues-hits-supplies-in-tribal-areas%2Farticleshow%2F102950173.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Edeclared%20an%20%E2%80%98economic%20blockade%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20highway%2C%20a%20lifeline%20of%20sorts%20for%20essential%20goods%20to%20the%20valley%20areas.%20At%20several%20times%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20said%20that%20it%20has%20cleared%20the%20road%20from%20such%20a%20blockade%20which%20the%20drivers%20and%20transporters%E2%80%99%20association%20contradict.%20Media%20reports%20have%20continuously%20highlighted%20that%20the%20Kuki%20groups%20reimpose%20the%20blockade%20thus%20snapping%20an%20important%20road%20route%20to%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Sunday%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20too%2C%20these%20associations%20once%20again%20urged%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20concerned%20authorities%20to%20resolve%20the%20matter%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20earliest%E2%80%9D%2C%20citing%20a%20looming%20crisis%20for%20petrol%20and%20LPG%20supply%20in%20the%20valley%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20associations%20have%20been%20on%20strike%20now%20demanding%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20to%20ensure%20their%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20memorandum%20submitted%20to%20several%20persons%20in%20the%20government%20including%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20the%20security%20advisor%20after%20the%20joint%20meeting%2C%20the%20valley-based%20petroleum%20fraternity%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20our%20sincere%20request%20to%20resume%20supply%20of%20fuel%20to%20the%20retail%20outlets%2C%20drivers%2Fdrivers%E2%80%99%20associations%20are%20determined%20to%20continue%20the%20strike%20until%20their%20demand%20to%20the%20Government%20for%20protection%20and%20safety%20is%20fulfilled.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20very%20serious%20crisis%20of%20petroleum%20products%20in%20the%20State%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesangaiexpress.com%2FEncyc%2F2023%2F10%2F16%2FBy-Our-Staff-ReporterIMPHAL-Oct-15-Highlighting-the-crippling-impact-of-the-cease-work-strike-being-under.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESangai%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20from%20the%20memorandum.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697440832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F13113152%2FF8LBinRaoAAaWqN.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-petrol-lpg-dealers-warn-of-looming-crisis-if-highway-blockades-continue%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20government%20has%20said%20it%20has%20cleared%20the%20blockade%20and%20provided%20security%20to%20petrol%20transporters%2C%20dealers%20and%20drivers%20say%20they%20continue%20to%20struggle.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-petrol-lpg-dealers-warn-of-looming-crisis-if-highway-blockades-continue%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cricket%20World%20Cup%3A%20The%20Good%20and%20the%20Ugly%20of%20a%20Hysterical%20Crowd%E2%80%99s%20Collective%20Energy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16120017%2FF8aUFslaYAAL2LJ.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Extra%20Cover%E2%80%99%20is%20veteran%20journalist%20Pradeep%20Magazine%E2%80%99s%20column%20on%20the%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20part%20of%20a%20multitude%2C%20bursting%20with%20energy%20and%20unbridled%20enthusiasm%2C%20screaming%20their%20lungs%20out%20as%20if%20in%20orgiastic%20ecstasy%20can%20be%20an%20uplifting%20experience%2C%20if%20you%20are%20one%20of%20them.%20It%20can%20be%20very%20scary%20if%20you%20are%20just%20an%20observer%20and%20not%20a%20participant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20had%20forgotten%20what%20it%20feels%20like%20watching%20India%20play%20a%20cricket%20match%2C%20that%20too%20in%20a%20World%20Cup.%20After%20the%202008%20IPL%20opening%20match%20in%20Bangalore%2C%20I%20have%20limited%20my%20watching%20experience%20mostly%20to%20the%20television%20set.%20Watching%20India%20play%20Afghanistan%20at%20the%20Kotla%20(sorry%20Arun%20Jaitley)%20Stadium%20last%20Wednesday%20from%20the%20western%20stands%20was%20like%20reliving%20a%20past%20and%20getting%20reminded%20of%20the%20hypnotic%20power%20of%20the%20collective%20energy%20of%20a%20hysterical%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndiaaa%2C%20Indiaa.%20Rooohiiit%2C%20Rooohiit.%20Buuumraaah%2C%20Buumraah.%20Thousands%20would%20join%20the%20call%20of%20one%20person%2C%20and%20the%20shout%20would%20spread%20across%20the%20entire%20stadium%20like%20wildfire%2C%20impossible%20to%20gauge%20where%20it%20began%20and%20where%20it%20will%20end.%20%E2%80%98Kohlii%2C%20Kohlii%E2%80%99%20was%20the%20default%20mode%20of%20a%20young%20crowd%20who%20would%20be%20screaming%20these%20names%2C%20as%20if%20in%20a%20trance.%20Each%20time%20the%20oval-shaped%20stadium%2C%20packed%20to%20the%20rafters%2C%20would%20erupt%2C%20you%20could%20feel%20the%20tremors%20of%20an%20earthquake%20shaking%20the%20ground%20beneath%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20treated%20to%20a%20sumptuous%20feast%20of%20batting%20skills%2C%20especially%20from%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20the%20majesty%20of%20whose%20batting%20and%20lightning%20footwork%20can%20only%20be%20observed%20and%20enjoyed%20while%20watching%20him%20bat%20live.%20In%20sheer%20elegance%2C%20decision-making%20and%20self-belief%20even%20the%20great%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20no%20match%20to%20him.%20In%20this%20form%2C%20he%20seems%20unstoppable.%20No%20wonder%20he%20went%20on%20to%20decimate%20the%20Pakistani%20bowling%20and%20looks%20set%20for%20many%20encores%20this%20World%20Cup.%20That%20is%20what%20an%20Indian%20fan%20will%20hope%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20overpowering%20noise%20of%20around%2040%2C000%20spectators%20is%20like%20a%20loud%20thunder%20drowning%20all%20voices%20supporting%20the%20rival%20team%2C%20one%20can%20well%20imagine%20what%20devastation%20a%20crowd%20of%20more%20than%20a%20lakh%20can%20have%20on%20the%20rival%20team.%20In%20Ahmedabad%2C%20this%20thunder%20must%20have%20sounded%20like%20a%20tornado%2C%20sweeping%20away%20all%20opposition%20voices%2C%20if%20any%2C%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20Kotla%2C%20there%20were%20a%20couple%20of%20spectators%20holding%20the%20Afghanistan%20flag.%20They%20were%20best%20left%20ignored%2C%20even%20then%20one%20of%20them%20was%20heckled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20magnificent%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%2C%20the%20crowds%20were%20treated%20to%20another%20delicious%20buffet%20of%20juicy%20morsels%2C%20with%20the%20very%20unorthodox%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20displaying%20those%20impossible%20geometrical%20angles%20from%20his%20wrists%20and%20arms%20that%20are%20bemusing%20the%20best%20of%20batsmen%20across%20the%20cricketing%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16120006%2FF8dDIfMW4AA2Xuf.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16120006%2FF8dDIfMW4AA2Xuf.jpeg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16120006%2FF8dDIfMW4AA2Xuf-300x210.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16120006%2FF8dDIfMW4AA2Xuf-1024x717.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680288%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22756%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIndian%20fans%20at%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20stadium%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20match%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20October%2014%2C%202023.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40cricketworldcup%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20watch%20him%20feels%20like%20one%20is%20watching%20a%20robot%20who%20can%20twist%20and%20bend%20his%20body%20in%20his%20bowling%20action%20without%20losing%20pace%2C%20swing%2C%20seam%20and%20control.%20He%20does%20not%20snarl%20or%20scream.%20He%20does%20all%20this%20with%20calm%20and%20a%20benign%20smile%2C%20a%20very%20unusual%20trait%20in%20times%20when%20macho%20aggression%20is%20the%20lifeline%20of%20our%20and%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20body%20politic.%20Bumrah%20could%20well%20be%20a%20welcome%20winning%20mascot%20for%20India%20in%20this%20World%20Cup%2C%20defying%20all%20those%20who%20seek%20energy%20from%20the%20display%20of%20visceral%20hatred%20of%20the%20other%20to%20succeed%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETelling%20strikes%20from%20Bumrah%20and%20the%20very%20enthusiastic%20Mohammad%20Siraj%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20match%20seemed%20headed%20for%20a%20very%20combative%20duel%20just%20drained%20all%20the%20energy%20from%20the%20Pakistan%20team.%20It%20was%20as%20if%20an%20air-tight%20balloon%20was%20pricked%20by%20a%20sharp%20needle%20and%20collapsed%20in%20a%20heap.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20Rohit%20took%20over.%20This%20supremely%20gifted%20batsman%20and%20a%20very%20wise%20captain%20who%20not%20only%20capitalises%20on%20an%20opportunity%20on%20offer%20but%20also%20creates%20them%20through%20his%20aggressive%20captaincy%2C%20once%20again%20unleashed%20strokes%20of%20brute%20power%2C%20executed%20with%20finesse%20and%20elegance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20can%20imagine%20and%20even%20recreate%20in%20my%20mind%E2%80%99s%20eye%20what%20the%20thousands%20and%20thousands%20at%20the%20Ahmedabad%20stadium%20must%20have%20felt%20while%20watching%20India%20cruise%20to%20a%20victory%2C%20something%20that%20most%20Indians%20believed%20was%20destined%20to%20happen.%20The%20celebratory%20sloganeering%2C%20a%20laudable%20object%20of%20a%20sports%20fan%2C%20is%20not%20to%20be%20denied%20to%20a%20highly%20charged%20partisan%20crowd.%20Its%20collective%20voice%20in%20a%20stadium%20is%20like%20nuclear%20energy%20that%20can%20uplift%20your%20team%20but%20what%20is%20distasteful%20is%20to%20target%20the%20rival%20team%20with%20objectionable%20slogans.%20It%20is%20reprehensible%20to%20taunt%20them%20for%20their%20religion%20and%20boo%20them%20wh