%20incredible%20as%20it%20may%20sound%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330088%2Fkerala-architect-designer-anupa-kurian-renovates-century-old-ancestral-home-sustainable-upcycle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKerala-based%20architect%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20turning%20this%20into%20a%20reality.%20The%20home%20located%20in%20Kozhikode%20serves%20as%20a%20weekend%20getaway%20for%20Kerala-based%20Dr%20Jayakumar%20and%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20technology%2C%20although%20unfamiliar%20to%20many%2C%20is%20not%20entirely%20new.%20It%20is%20already%20in%20use%20in%20many%20countries%2C%20including%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Majid%20TK%2C%20the%20architect%20behind%20this%20innovative%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20technology%20is%20known%20as%20Light%20Gauge%20Steel%20Frame%20(LGSF)%20technology%2C%20which%20uses%20cold-formed%20steel%20as%20the%20primary%20construction%20material.%20This%20frame%20can%20be%20used%20for%20the%20walls%2C%20roofs%2C%20decks%2C%20or%20even%20for%20the%20entire%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%20might%20sound%20a%20bit%20unusual%2C%20homes%20constructed%20using%20this%20technology%20are%20not%20only%20eco-friendlier%20than%20traditional%20homes%20but%20are%20also%20more%20resilient%20in%20the%20face%20of%20disasters%20and%20require%20less%20time%20for%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Majid.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStill%20left%20with%20questions%20and%20doubts%3F%20Well%20Majid%20sits%20down%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20to%20address%20all%20of%20our%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPack%20your%20home%20and%20take%20it%20anywhere%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20founder%20of%20ODF%20Group%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323054%2Fbengaluru-architects-build-zero-waste-sustainable-euroschool-near-n