kshmi%20Machine%20Works%20in%20Coimbatore%2C%20where%20he%20developed%20a%20deep%20interest%20in%20aerospace%20engineering.%20Subsequently%2C%20he%20worked%20in%20the%20research%20and%20development%20division%20of%20the%20helicopter%20division%20of%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20Limited%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331067%2Framji-swaminathan-craftizan-miniature-models-of-isro-rockets-satellites-chandrayaan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesign%20engineer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20dreamt%20of%20working%20in%20ISRO%20since%20his%20college%20days%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20ISRO%20Satellite%20Centre%20as%20a%20project%20engineer%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20worked%20on%20multiple%20remote%20sensing%20and%20scientific%20satellites%2C%20and%20with%20the%20Mars%20Orbiter%20Mission%20in%202013.%20He%20also%20enrolled%20in%20a%20PhD%20at%20IIT%20Madras%20to%20fuel%20his%20love%20for%20research%20after%20joining%20ISRO.%20His%20doctorate%20is%20on%20the%20topic%20%E2%80%98Vibration%20Suppression%20of%20Electronic%20Package%20in%20Satellites%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVeeramuthuvel%20led%20ISRO%E2%80%99s%20inaugural%20nanosatellite%20team%2C%20successfully%20launching%20three%20of%20them.%20With%20a%20team%20of%20young%20scientists%2C%20all%20under%20the%20age%20of%2040%2C%20they%20achieved%20this%20feat%20in%20just%20nine%20months%2C%20propelling%20Veeramuthuvel%20to%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%2015%20to%2020%20%5Bscientists%5D%20and%20they%20came%20up%20with%20a%20bus%20configuration%20for%20the%20project%2C%20which%20was%20launched%20around%202017.%20This%20was%20the%20time%20we%20saw%20his%20leadership%20qualities%20and%20that%20helped%20him%20emerge%20as%20the%20project%20director%20after%20the%20failure%20of%20Chandrayaan-2%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20former%20ISRO%20scientist%20and%20sate